# I have successfully moved back to the stone furnace's location.
# 
# Now, I will insert the 10 iron ore into the furnace for smelting, along with some coal to ensure it has enough fuel to operate.

insert_item(Prototype.IronOre, furnace, quantity=10)  # Inserting 10 iron ore into the stone furnace.
insert_item(Prototype.Coal, furnace, quantity=5)  # Inserting 5 coal into the stone furnace for fuel.
